### ========================================
### GET - All tickets (no filter)
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets

### ========================================
### GET - Filter by status = Open
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?status=Open

### ========================================
### GET - Filter by status = Closed
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?status=Closed

### ========================================
### GET - Filter by priority = High
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?priority=High

### ========================================
### GET - Filter by priority = Medium
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?priority=Medium

### ========================================
### GET - Filter by priority = Low
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?priority=Low

### ========================================
### GET - Filter by category = Bug
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?category=Bug

### ========================================
### GET - Filter by category = Feature Request
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?category=Feature%20Request

### ========================================
### GET - Filter by category = Documentation
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?category=Documentation

### ========================================
### GET - One ticket by ID (replace with real ID from GET /api/tickets above)
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID

### ========================================
### GET - Missing ticket (should return 404)
### ========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/000000000000000000000000

### ========================================
### POST - Create a valid ticket
### ========================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cannot connect to VPN",
  "description": "VPN connection fails with timeout error",
  "category": "Network",
  "priority": "High",
  "createdBy": "alice@example.com"
}

### ========================================
### POST - Create an invalid ticket (empty fields - should return 400)
### ========================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "",
  "category": "",
  "priority": "",
  "createdBy": ""
}
